title: Textiles and ornaments of India (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
MoMA | 1956 | Pdf | Eng | 95 p | ISBN:10 040501564X | 12.9 MB

Textiles and ornaments of India - a selection of designs 
edited, with a foreword, by Monroe Wheeler [director of the exhibition]
Texts by Pupul Jayakar and John Irwin.

This publication - a picture book with interpretive essays is based on an exhibition held at the Museum of Modern Art in the spring and summer of 1955
